description: Conversation Starter is a great way to get suggested conversation topics for you and your friends. For example, asking Conversation Starter for a topic might suggest talking about your greatest fear, the best day of your life, or something you would change if given the chance.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Conversation Starter for a topic
"next" (can be stated after Alexa provides a conversation topic)
name: Conversation Starter
